bm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/4a3038c8e977de01a755535dac76fd57.mp4?t=1773262413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Although the game is marked <strong>Adults Only</strong>, the main focus has always been on the <strong>story</strong>. However, when it comes to adult scenes - no static images everything is animated. The rest goes without saying. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/67b306d36778ef2e5e3bfee2dd9e23dd.poster.avif?t=1773262413\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/67b306d36778ef2e5e3bfee2dd9e23dd.webm?t=1773262413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/67b306d36778ef2e5e3bfee2dd9e23dd.mp4?t=1773262413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/37c3bf33e9c5a2a76bc25224a4612216.poster.avif?t=1773262413\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/37c3bf33e9c5a2a76bc25224a4612216.webm?t=1773262413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/37c3bf33e9c5a2a76bc25224a4612216.mp4?t=1773262413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sherine Hale, an undercover CIA operative, is assigned a high-stakes mission targeting a wealthy Russian oligarch. Tasked with infiltrating his inner circle and installing spy software on his home network, Sherine finds herself in perilous scenarios, navigating tense confrontations and tricky dilemmas. The stakes are high amid the competitive oil business, where massive fortunes are at play. In these difficult situations, not only her wits come in handy—Sherine must also rely on her resourcefulness, quick thinking, and adaptability to survive. Drawing on her sharp mind, deductive skills, and charm, she maneuvers through encounters with shady figures in the oil industry. Players guide her key decisions, shaping her path between success and failure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The demo of the game is live. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features a unique cinematic experience with an optional <i>Movie Mode</i>. In this mode, dialogues flow naturally—just like in a film—while still allowing you to make important choices along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/c6cb62b5977ce19d9883d3132b91fd37.poster.avif?t=1773262413\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/c6cb62b5977ce19d9883d3132b91fd37.webm?t=1773262413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/c6cb62b5977ce19d9883d3132b91fd37.mp4?t=1773262413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every image in the game is <strong>fully animated</strong>, creating a seamless and dynamic visual flow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/2143044478dc3ac7f218dec053028ab6.poster.avif?t=1773262413\" width=800 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/2143044478dc3ac7f218dec053028ab6.webm?t=1773262413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/2143044478dc3ac7f218dec053028ab6.mp4?t=1773262413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combined with advanced lip-sync technology, this brings characters and scenes to life, making the experience feel truly cinematic.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/96b92301c68444b87ee6615a5e6ee157.poster.avif?t=1773262413\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/96b92301c68444b87ee6615a5e6ee157.webm?t=1773262413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/96b92301c68444b87ee6615a5e6ee157.mp4?t=1773262413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/4a3038c8e977de01a755535dac76fd57.poster.avif?t=1773262413\" width=800 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/4a3038c8e977de01a755535dac76fd57.webm?t=1773262413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/4a3038c8e977de01a755535dac76fd57.mp4?t=1773262413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Although the game is marked <strong>Adults Only</strong>, the main focus has always been on the <strong>story</strong>. However, when it comes to adult scenes - no static images everything is animated. The rest goes without saying. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/67b306d36778ef2e5e3bfee2dd9e23dd.poster.avif?t=1773262413\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/67b306d36778ef2e5e3bfee2dd9e23dd.webm?t=1773262413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/67b306d36778ef2e5e3bfee2dd9e23dd.mp4?t=1773262413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/37c3bf33e9c5a2a76bc25224a4612216.poster.avif?t=1773262413\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/37c3bf33e9c5a2a76bc25224a4612216.webm?t=1773262413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3910920/extras/37c3bf33e9c5a2a76bc25224a4612216.mp4?t=1773262413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>", "short_description": "CIA operative Sherine Hale infiltrates a Russian oligarch’s world to install spy software. Facing danger in the high-stakes oil business, she relies on wits, charm, and resourcefulness. Players guide her choices, balancing success and failure in tense encounters.", "support